Named after one of Taylor’s original founders, the Yeatman is Porto\'s only true five-star resort, terraced and tucked into the Gaia
        hillside with expansive Douro and Porto views. There’s a Michelin-starred chef; huge, sumptuous guest rooms and suites with private terraces; a decanter-shaped pool;
        sunken Roman baths in the fantastic Caudalie spa; and close to everything else you could possibly wish for.
